<section class="student-section">
	<h2>Welcome to ACM at Allegheny</h2>
	<p>We're a community of students passionate about computing, technology, and innovation. Through events, workshops, and collaboration, we work together to build skills, create connections, and make an impact on our campus and beyond.</p>
